p: Analysis revealed an increase in the proportion of A(H1N1)pdm09 influenza virus detected in lethal influenza cases (65%) compared to equal proportions of A(H1N1)pdm09, A(H3N2) and influenza B viruses in all influenza cases. A similar increased proportion of A(H1N1)pdm09 compared with A(H3N2) detected in lethal cases compared to all cases was observed in Europe [ 31].
